1. *Videti* ga je bilo zaista neverovatno! (Seeing him was really unbelievable!)
2. Nismo mogli da *vidimo* kako je stvarno izgledao. (We couldn't see how he really looked like.)
3. Nismo mogli da *vidimo* njegovo lice. (We couldn't see his face.)
4. On je bio u stanju da *vidi* sve što se dešavalo. (He was able to see everything that was happening.)
5. *Videti* ga je bilo zastrašujuće. (Seeing him was frightening.)
6. *Videći* ga, svi su se začudili. (Seeing him, everyone was surprised.)